text: *For the WWE brand/TV Show, see WWE Raw. Foods are raw when they are not cooked. Most things are safe to eat raw, but some of them can be poisonous. ==Health== There's currently no solid evidence to suggest that raw food is more healthy than cooked food. ===Germs=== Raw food can sometimes make people sick because of bacteria which would otherwise be killed by cooking. Category:Food and drink
title: Raw food
